Insider Activity


Individual




Stephen J. Sipola



Mr. Stephen J. Sipola is Executive Vice President at Astoria Financial Corp. and EVP & Managing Director-Business Banking Group at Astoria Bank. He is on the Board of Directors at Long Island Association, Inc., American Heart Association, Inc., and The Long Island Home.
He received his undergraduate degree from New York University and an MBA from New York University.



